## Database Setup Commands (After First Deploy)

Run these after deploying to Vercel:

```bash
# Option A: Using Vercel CLI (Recommended)
npm install -g vercel
vercel login
vercel link
cd server
vercel env pull .env.local
npm install
npm run db:generate
npm run db:push
npm run db:seed

# Or Option B: Using the connection string directly
cd server
echo "DATABASE_URL=postgresql://neondb_owner:npg_0O3HvkmbwBFP@ep-misty-boat-agvim722-pooler.c-2.eu-central-1.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require&channel_binding=require" > .env
echo "JWT_SECRET=MRnOEAPp6zfu62utyUqo2evMC3sLtAcov5vrky6LbQDdJdQ0Q8mZ/o4lgocDiES1" >> .env
npm install
npm run db:generate
npm run db:push
npm run db:seed
```

