## Quick Deployment Steps

### 1. Deploy to Vercel
- Go to https://vercel.com
- Import inara-hub-v3 repository
- Configure project (Framework: Other, Build: `npm run install:all && npm run build`)
- Add environment variables from above
- Click Deploy

### 2. After Deploy
- Note your Vercel URL (e.g., https://inara-hub-v3-abc123.vercel.app)
- Update CORS_ORIGIN in Vercel to your actual URL
- Redeploy

### 3. Initialize Database
- Run the commands above (Option A recommended)

### 4. Test
- Visit https://your-app.vercel.app/api/health
- Login with admin@inara.org / admin123
- Test file upload

